title: New Zealand beats Georgia 43-10, advances at Rugby World Cup
text:
Published By: Charlotte Observer: Sports - Today 
New Zealand ran in seven tries, dispatched Georgia 43-10 for a third straight pool win, and became the first team to qualify for the quarter...
